!!!Safari

In Safari, you can enable a hidden 'develop' menu by going to Safari -> Preferences -> Advanced and selecting the appropriate option.

From the develop menu you can then launch the 'web inspector' or the 'javascript console' and the developer tools will open at the bottom of the screen.